data.description: Welcome to this beautiful one story ranch on over half acre corner lot with an enjoyable rocking chair front porch. Charming foyer entry which leads to large family room with gorgeous wood look tile, vaulted ceilings, gas starter wood burning fireplace. Separate spacious formal dining room with eat in kitchen area, granite counter tops, backsplash, top of the line stainless steel appliances (Asko energy efficiency/extra quiet dishwasher, Kitchen Aid counter top depth refrigerator and gas double oven and stove). Master on main with double vanity, separate shower, garden tub and walk in closet. Extra large bonus room over the garage with separate entry. Fenced in back yard with covered patio and a shed with power. Plus additional side concrete parking for RV or boat with 50 amp 240 service for additional power. HVAC approximately four years old, Ecobee smart thermostat and newer PEX plumbing approx. 2yrs, Convenient to interstate 475 and shopping. Call today for a showing to make this your home!
